content: I don't have access to every detail of take that's tours with robbie williams. however, according to reports, their 2019 "greatest hits live" tour featured mostly their biggest hits from their long career, as well as some of robbie williams' most famous solo tracks. it did not feature any new songs besides the band's 2018 single "out of our heads," which was performed during the tour. the focus of the tour was to celebrate the band's legacy and reunite with robbie williams, rather than promoting new material.
